            "title": "A股低開後跌幅擴大",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股低開後跌幅擴大，創業板跌逾1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指今早開跌8點或0.19%，報4081點。現跌20點或0.5%，報4072點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指今早開跌92點或0.61%，報14951點。現跌90點或0.6%，報14953點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數開跌15點或0.31%，報4771點。現跌19點或0.4%，報4766點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數開跌1.02%或38點，報3682點。現跌38點或1.03%，報3681點。</p>\n</div>",
