            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指開報 25803 ，跌118點或0.46%，低水112點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科指期貨開報4834，跌33點或0.68%，低水32點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國指期貨開報8702，跌33點或0.38%，低水31點。</p>\n</div>",
